вЂ‹Low Data Footprint: 
The ticketing system uses text-based data and optimized image uploads (limited to 2MB-5MB), making it accessible for students on small data bundles.

вЂ‹Firebase Storage Logic: 
You will implement a 30-day auto-delete for resolved tickets to keep your storage costs at near-zero.

вЂ‹Scalability: 
Because the roles are dynamic, you can sell this same codebase to a 10-student center or a 5,000-student college.





